102
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:29,090
No way.

103
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:30,679
Do you know how many years

104
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:31,719
I have to act

105
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:33,130
