106
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:35,610
So why won't you let me act
and pay you back?

107
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:45,530
I get it.

108
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:47,930
You're jealous.

109
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:51,410
You don't want me acting
with Su Yuling, do you?

110
00:06:53,400 --> 00:06:55,210
Me? Jealous?

111
00:06:56,080 --> 00:06:57,079
Impossible.

112
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:58,119
And besides, Su Yuling...

113
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,610
She's not even worthy.

114
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:05,239
Then why won't you let me act

115
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:07,010
and make money to pay you back?

116
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:15,610
You...

117
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,610
Do you like me?

118
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,039
I...

119
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:20,439
That's ridiculous.

120
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:21,479
No matter what,

121
