129
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:46,439
Lidong needs to come to the company.

130
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:47,850
Are you out of your mind?

131
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:53,919
Wait, Ms. Lin.

132
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:56,399
You know
what condition Yan Lidong is in.

133
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:58,210
I need to see him by noon tomorrow!

134
00:08:00,080 --> 00:08:00,970
I...

135
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:03,519
Chairman.

136
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,999
All the shareholders are here.

137
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,479
They've been waiting outside for ages.

138
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:07,639
Let them in.

139
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:08,639
